    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a \"phase\" or something that goes away with a therapist. it feels more fundamental than that. like the core of me—the artist—is dead. if the thing that made me *me* is gone, then what am i even doing here? i'm just occupying space. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting my own body.",
